datasets.name: 39a5402c
queryLines:
-- CTE to get the top 5 topics by the number of tickets
WITH TopTopics AS (
  SELECT
    Topic
  FROM
    main.samples.technical_support_dataset
  GROUP BY
    Topic
  ORDER BY
    COUNT(`Ticket ID`) DESC
  LIMIT
    5
), -- CTE to get the top 4 countries by the number of tickets
TopCountries AS (
  SELECT
    Country
  FROM
    main.samples.technical_support_dataset
  GROUP BY
    Country
  ORDER BY
    COUNT(`Ticket ID`) DESC
  LIMIT
    4
) -- Main query to select data from the technical support dataset
SELECT
  *,
  -- Calculate the resolution time in hours, adding a random adjustment for Tier 2 support level
  (
    TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, `Created time`, `Resolution time`) + CASE
      WHEN `Support Level` = 'Tier 2' THEN FLOOR(3000 + (RAND() * (3000 - 2400)))
      ELSE 0
    END
  ) / 60.0 AS `Resolution Time`
FROM
  main.samples.technical_support_dataset -- Filter to include only tickets with top topics
WHERE
  Topic IN (
    SELECT
      Topic
    FROM
      TopTopics
  ) -- Filter to include only tickets from top countries
  AND Country IN (
    SELECT
      Country
    FROM
      TopCountries
  ) -- Exclude tickets where the resolution time is zero
  AND TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, `Created time`, `Resolution time`) != 0

datasets.name: 916033f4
queryLines:
SELECT Country, COUNT(`Ticket ID`) AS Support_Volume
FROM main.samples.technical_support_dataset
GROUP BY Country

datasets.name: 44cccafd
queryLines:
SELECT Topic, COUNT(`Ticket ID`) AS Support_Volume, 
       (COUNT(`Ticket ID`) * 100.0 / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM main.samples.technical_support_dataset)) AS Percentage
FROM main.samples.technical_support_dataset
GROUP BY Topic

datasets.name: 56d2ee72
queryLines:
SELECT 
  SUM(CASE WHEN Status = 'In progress' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS In_Progress_Tickets,
  SUM(CASE WHEN Status = 'Closed' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Closed_Tickets,
  SUM(CASE WHEN Status = 'Resolved' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Resolved_Tickets
FROM main.samples.technical_support_dataset
